00:24:01,999 --> 00:24:04,999
But when there is ego, you cannot have common sense.

298
00:24:05,280 --> 00:24:07,200
And this is the reason I think

299
00:24:07,440 --> 00:24:11,440
the western people have become so stupid in so many things.

300
00:24:12,160 --> 00:24:15,240
Whatever I see, I see it's upside down.

301
00:24:15,480 --> 00:24:18,320
Indians, we may be poor people, in the villages.

302
00:24:18,480 --> 00:24:21,840
They are not so educated. You are all very well educated people,

303
00:24:21,999 --> 00:24:25,999
everything is there, but all has come out of ego.

304
00:24:26,999 --> 00:24:29,999
So the common sense is lacking.

305
00:24:32,960 --> 00:24:35,320
So those who deal with the Mother Earth, like farmers are,

306
00:24:35,480 --> 00:24:38,400
have tremendous common sense.

307
00:24:39,160 --> 00:24:42,320
Now in Holland I used to think people will have

308
00:24:42,480 --> 00:24:45,480
lot of common sense, because they are farmers you see.

309
00:24:46,320 --> 00:24:49,960
When I had come in '65, they were better off, much better people,

310
00:24:50,120 --> 00:24:52,400
not so nonsensical.

