could not get anything made in Holland.

316
00:25:09,400 --> 00:25:12,320
So I said, "How is it? You don't make anything, machines?"

317
00:25:12,480 --> 00:25:16,000
They said, "Why should we? For our twenty-five bulbs of tulips,

318
00:25:16,280 --> 00:25:20,840
- in those days - we get one transistor from Japan.

319
00:25:20,999 --> 00:25:24,999
So why should we make a transistor?"  Common sense.

320
00:25:25,999 --> 00:25:28,240
"We send from here twenty five bulbs".

321
00:25:28,480 --> 00:25:32,960
And they had fields and fields of all kinds of tulips,

322
00:25:33,120 --> 00:25:35,840
all over, I mean when I came here. So they said,

323
00:25:36,000 --> 00:25:39,320
"For twenty-five bulbs we get one transistor so why should we?

324
00:25:39,480 --> 00:25:43,999
We export our bulbs to them and get their transistors.

325
00:25:44,440 --> 00:25:47,999
Why should we make transistors?"

326
00:25:49,999 --> 00:25:53,000
Then they said "We export our cheese to a particular country,

327
00:25:53,400 --> 00:25:56,320
our eggs to Italy , our chicken to this country

328
00:25:56,480 --> 00:25:58,999
and we get all that we need."

329
00:26:00,000 --> 00:26:05,840
I was amazed you see. They are so, so proud of their agriculture

330
00:26:05,999 --> 00:26:07,840
and so much doing that way,

331
00:26:07,999 --> 00:26:10,240
which was a very sensible thing and because

332
00:26:10,440 --> 00:26:12,999
they were dealing with the land I thought I'll find

333
00:26:13,240 --> 00:26:15,960
Holland people to be the best.

334
00:26:16,440 --> 00:26:18,320
But then I got reports that people are

335
00:26:18,480 --> 00:26:21,000
absolutely gone off their heads.

336
00:26:21,360 --> 00:26:24,999
They have become like bullocks now

337
00:26:27,920 --> 00:26:31,120
Working with the land they have become

338
00:26:31,320 --> 00:26:33,999
like bullocks who plough the land.

339
00:26:34,480 --> 00:26:38,999
I was surprised "How have they become like bulls?"

340
00:26:39,999 --> 00:26:43,400
They were very sensible people, very sensible.

341
00:26:44,000 --> 00:26:48,999
Farmers, sensibly dealing with things

342
00:26:49,999 --> 00:26:52,480
and working out things

343
00:26:53,480 --> 00:26:55,999
in such a beautiful manner,

344
00:26:56,480 --> 00:27:00,960
very innocent and simple people and naive,

345
00:27:01,360 --> 00:27:05,320
up to a point of sweetness, very sweet.

346
00:27:05,480 --> 00:27:08,320
When we came here they wanted to please us,

347
00:27:08,480 --> 00:27:12,480
so they wanted to put a flag for us or for our country.

