00:27:12,999 --> 00:27:15,999
And they put Pakistan's flag in front of us.

349
00:27:25,999 --> 00:27:28,840
So I was very happy to see that.

350
00:27:28,999 --> 00:27:31,280
And they were talking of vegetarianism.

351
00:27:31,480 --> 00:27:34,280
But when we came, my daughter had suddenly become vegetarian

352
00:27:34,480 --> 00:27:36,320
because she had developed a funny nausea

353
00:27:36,480 --> 00:27:38,960
in the, in the ship, you see.

354
00:27:39,120 --> 00:27:41,000
So she was not eating any meat or like that.

355
00:27:41,280 --> 00:27:43,840
So she said "We are, I am vegetarian".

356
00:27:44,000 --> 00:27:47,999
So they said, "All right, then will you have chicken?"

357
00:27:48,200 --> 00:27:51,999
They were that simple you know, very simple people.

358
00:27:52,920 --> 00:27:54,840
And now they are talking about vegetarianism.

