and in the next station the chicken is selling for one pound,

377
00:29:15,120 --> 00:29:17,320
what is my age?"

378
00:29:17,480 --> 00:29:19,960
Just to tease him.

379
00:29:20,160 --> 00:29:24,480
So immediately the fellow says "You must be twenty-two".

